com.paypal.selion.grid.servlets.transfer

Class DefaultManagedArtifact

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.grid.servlets.transfer.DefaultManagedArtifact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManagedArtifact

    public class DefaultManagedArtifact
extends Object
implements ManagedArtifact
    DefaultManagedArtifact represents an artifact that is successfully saved to SeLion grid by an HTTP POST method call. This artifact mostly represents binary file types rather than text files. The MIME type for this artifact is set to 'application/zip'. Expiration of the artifact is based on TTL (Time To Live) specified in milliseconds The configuration is read from Grid configuration system.
